column2: SELECT TOP # s.specObjID,s.ra, s.dec,  s.psfMag_g-s.extinction_g AS psf_mag_g,  s.psfMag_r-s.extinction_r AS psf_mag_r,  s.psfMag_i-s.extinction_i AS psf_mag_i,  s.psfMag_z-s.extinction_z AS psf_mag_z  FROM Star AS s JOIN SpecObjAll AS p ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID WHERE (s.psfMag_g-s.extinction_g)<# AND (s.psfMag_g-s.extinction_g)># AND (s.psfMag_r-s.extinction_r)<# AND (s.psfMag_r-s.extinction_r)># AND (s.psfMag_i-s.extinction_i)<# AND (s.psfMag_i-s.extinction_i)># AND (s.psfMag_z-s.extinction_z)<# AND (s.psfMag_z-s.extinction_z)># AND p.class = &&& AND p.sciencePrimary=# AND s.ra > # and s.ra < # AND s.dec > # and s.dec < #
